{"title":"2021-03-07 取立山","virttualPath":null,"html":"<div class=\"markdown-body\"><h1>\n<a id=\"user-content-2021-03-07-取立山\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#2021-03-07-%E5%8F%96%E7%AB%8B%E5%B1%B1\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\"></span></a>2021-03-07 取立山</h1>\n<p>取立山に登ってきた。久々にでかいミスして死ぬかと思ったぜ。ドキドキ…\n移動距離は 21km 獲得標高は 1538m</p>\n<p>ここは大長山(おおちょうさん) 取立山のさらに奥。この日はいっぱい来てた。</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"2021-03-07/20210307-094336-ricoh360.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"2021-03-07/20210307-094336-ricoh360.jpg\" alt=\"myimage://2021/2021-03-07/20210307-094336-ricoh360.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p><strong>加筆中</strong></p>\n<p>白峰総湯は何度きてもよい。ぬるっとする。</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"2021-03-07/20210307-172432-P_20210307_172432.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"2021-03-07/20210307-172432-P_20210307_172432.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"白峰総湯\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>白山市の響に寄ってきた。久々にうまい。</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"2021-03-07/20210307-191436-P_20210307_191436.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"2021-03-07/20210307-191436-P_20210307_191436.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n</div>","styles":["/css/github-markdown.css","/css/markdown-include.css"],"description":"随筆","updated":"2021-03-07T21:23:27","published":"2021-03-07T05:58:29"}